cs.RO, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL 

This paper presents a method for generating optimal robot trajectories, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of temporal logic formulas and automata suggests a focus on logic and verification (cs.LO) as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the method to data gathering in a road network suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the use of graph algorithms suggests a focus on programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
